************************************** Operation WishList Test Steps**************************************************

WishList - share to a friend test1
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Go to Sign In page
4. Enter user name & password
5. Go to Women Clothing Tops and T-shirts category
6. Choose Tri Factor Top product (1st one)
7. Select "Small" for size
8. Press "add to wishlist" button
9. Press "share to a friend" button
10. Enter "aila.bogasieru@yahoo.com" email address


WishList - different operations test2
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Go to Sign In page
4. Enter user name & password
5. Go to Women Clothing Tops and T-shirts category
6. Choose Tri Factor Top product (1st one)
7. Select Small for "size"
8. Press "add to wishlist" button
9. Set for priority "Medium"
10. Increase qty to 3
11. Decrease qty to 2
12. Go to edit item from wishlist
13. Change the size into "Medium"
14. Press "update" button
15. Go back to wishlist
	
	

WishList - add to cart test3
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Go to Sign In page
4. Enter user name & password
5. Go to Women Clothing Tops and T-shirts category
6. Choose Tri Factor Top product (1st one)
7. Select Small for "size"
8. Press "add to wishlist" button
9. Press "Add to cart"



WishList - remove item from wishlist test4
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Go to Sign In page
4. Enter user name & password
5. Go to Women Clothing Tops and T-shirts category
6. Choose Tri Factor Top product (1st one)
7. Select Small for "size"
8. Press "add to wishlist" button
9. Press "remove" button
	